<paragraph pageId="189" pageNumber="190">
This species is similar to 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Cephaloleia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cephaloleia collaris" order="Coleoptera" pageId="189" pageNumber="190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="collaris">Cephaloleia collaris</taxonomicName>
