<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Cephaloleia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cephaloleia flavipennis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="189" pageNumber="190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavipennis">Cephaloleia flavipennis</taxonomicName>
. It can be distinguished by the transverse basal impression on the pronotum and the canalicultae lateral margins of the pronotum.
</paragraph>
